title: Tobenai Bokura wa Kaze wo Miru
original_name: 飛べない僕らは風を見る
sinopse:
A collection of one-shots.

1. Tobenai Bokura wa Kaze wo Miru
   My little sister becomes prettier with each passing summer. In my arms, she becomes even more beautiful. I have tasted the forbidden fruit and known its truth; I have no fear of anything. But why, even though I swore that...?!
   (Source: Midnight Scans)
